2.4.7.name: nervo/yuicompressor
2.4.7.description: YUI Compressor is an open source tool that supports the compression of both JavaScript and CSS files. The JavaScript compression removes comments and white-spaces as well as obfuscates local variables using the smallest possible variable name. CSS compression is done using a regular-expression-based CSS minifier.
